extendedInfo.description: The GRE High Frequency Flash Cards App is a handy tool to memorize words. It helps the preparation of SAT, TOEFL, CAT etc. as well. It is a simple app custom-tailored to suit your purpose of memorizing words. There is absolutely no learning curve. You tap a word see its meaning and recite, thats it. The word list contains high frequency words, meaning the ones that have appeared very frequently in GRE. The app can help you utilize your time during long travels etc. With this free tool at your finger tip, your success rate in GRE is bound to increase.
